>\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">一傳十十傳百</span></span></strong><br />\n唔自救大家玩L完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果喺之前個post比左總共超過600個like or dislike嘅朋友傳開去，好快會令全民醒覺！！<br />\n<strong>星火燎原</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2102947/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2102947/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我哋可以做咩嘢？</span></span></strong><br />\n1.話比身邊嘅人知香港有個後門大量吸收潛在冇病症感染者及傳播者。<br />\n<br />\n2.呼籲身邊所有人戴口罩，特別係果班唔肯帶嘅中年人<br />\n<br />\n3.如果身邊有料，可以報上傳媒比如蘋果。<br />\n例如喺之前post有其他人話知道：<br />\n灣仔入境個邊D移民公司而家當免檢疫証明係生意咁做，搵班阿姐派傳單幫人攪。<br />\n每日中港司機都幾千人出出入入。<br />\n<br />\n4.煲大件事！比全世界多D人知道，只有多D人覺醒，知道個政府係棄全香港巿民安危不顧，先會爭取到更多人企係我哋呢邊，同我哋一齊抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟姊妹各自爬山 他日平安相聚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n_________________________________________<br />\n為自己為身邊重要嘅人<br />\n請大家支持抗疫！！<br />\n我知道呢個世界好黑暗，但係唔可以就咁放棄架！<br />\n點對得住果班為左香港未來獻出性命同安危嘅朋友！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4bfca1fc65334d71ed67b66109f296c7b02477","tid":2114618,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1115f7c05ee47368ed51c59d3f874659ebba7dc1","tid":2114618,"uid":179825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"3e607aab4bcddb6d2a6a8d5e14f2b1d9542bbce1","tid":2114618,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94UV534.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai